Warp is in a developer-only beta phase through Fall 2020 as we work on the user interface.  The instructions below cover
setting up the API and will include full install instructions later. For now, we will assume some basic Python development and
command line skills.  As we evolve, these instructions will evolve to make them more accessible to everyone. If you would like
